</item>
<item>
<ptxt>Center airbag sensor assembly</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</entry>
</row>
<row>
<entry valign="middle" align="center">
<ptxt>B1812/53</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<list1 type="unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>The center airbag sensor assembly receives a short circuit to ground signal in the driver side 2nd step circuit for 0.5 seconds.</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>Driver side squib 2nd step malfunction</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>Spiral cable malfunction</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
